&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">The Omuro Zakura Garden at Ninnaji-temple. As the cherry blossoms fall to the ground and new leaves sprout, we are reaching the end of sakura season in Kyoto.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07528.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07528.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hikone Castle・彦根城</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220411/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hikone Castle・彦根城" /><published>2022-04-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hikone-castle</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220411/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
   Hikone Castle in the evening. Located east of Kyoto in Shiga Prefecture, &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hikone_Castle&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Hikone Castle&lt;/a&gt; is one of only 12 original castles in Japan (the others are modern reconstructions).
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    夜の彦根城。京都の東、滋賀県にある&lt;a href=&quot;https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%A6%E6%A0%B9%E5%9F%8E&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;彦根城&lt;/a&gt;は、日本に12しかないオリジナルの城の一つです（他は近代的な復元）。
&lt;/p&gt;
